 bgp log-neighbor-changes
 neighbor 30.0.0.15 remote-as 1001
 neighbor 2001:301:15:21::1 remote-as 1001
 neighbor 52.0.0.24 remote-as 520
 neighbor 2001:520:21:24::2 remote-as 520
