 neighbor 2001:0:21:22::2 remote-as 101
 !
 address-family ipv4
  neighbor 30.0.0.15 activate
  no neighbor 2001:301:15:21::1 activate
  neighbor 52.0.0.24 activate
  no neighbor 2001:520:21:24::2 activate
  no neighbor 2001:0:21:22::2 activate
 exit-address-family
 !
